embraced data as a critical business asset


all leading companies state in their annual reports and somewhere in their business mission statements that data is a critical business asset, that they are striving to become data-driven in their analysis and thinking, that they are deeply engaged in forging a data culture at all levels of their organization, and that they view data as a basis for innovation and competition in the global marketplace.   We have come a very long way in a few short decades. Times change.
